              },
              "displayName": "Bikas Saha",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "I like the idea of not using impersonation to achieve isolation. Would you mind sharing something about the approach/design before submitting patches. That would help shed some light and evoke discussion (better than a patch might IMO). Is the plan to continue to use winutils or create a new launcher executable?",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=bikassaha",
              "name": "bikassaha",
              "key": "bikassaha",
