              },
              "displayName": "Kyle Leckie",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Hi Bikas,\nI am currently adding the functionality to winutils. I have been prototyping an approach that launches the container with a low integrity level and an access token with restricted DACLS. I need to determine if this is sufficient. \nMy previous approach was launching the task as the submitting user without requiring credentials. This approach would be a mismatch for cloud deployments and on prem would require some domain administrator work. ",
